						The <term>conjunction</term> of <m>P</m> and <m>Q</m>, denoted <m>P \land Q</m> and read "<m>P</m> and <m>Q</m>", is true when both <m>P</m> and <m>Q</m> are true, and false otherwise. See <xref ref="table-and" />.
